			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-509074">
									

<p>Really, why are people freaking on this? It's a solid idea, and it's just descriptive enough to get your mind going without detailing anything truely digusting.</p>
<p>As for NSFW? er.. I consider the entire site to be read with discression. Most of these pages could cause the wrong person to panic. I mean, people see a brown bag unattended and next thing you know cops are detonating it, without even knowing the contents. This is the age of overreaction. So it is best not to look at things where others can see.</p>
<p>Meh, I just hope to see more odds and ends like this. They really add to the flavor.</p>

